			.row.mb-40
				.col.l6.m6.s12
					.page-title-wrapper(style="background-image:url(assets/images/about-us/main-courses-2.png)")
						h2.page-title.text-center ONLINE COURSES
					.title-st-2.uppercase.mt-20.mb-10(style='color:#444444;') Choose an online course if you:
					ul.list-st1.checked.content-p
						li.truncate-on-md have commitments like work, school etc
						li.truncate-on-md don't want a commute and set schedules
						li.truncate-on-md are looking for good value
						li.truncate-on-md want to get started right away
						li.truncate-on-md prefer job placement flexibility
						li.truncate-on-md are already on the road
					a.button-st1.full-width.uppercase.alt.text-orange.mt-30.mb-sm-40(href="#") view online courses >
				.col.l6.m6.s12
					.page-title-wrapper(style="background-image:url(assets/images/about-us/main-courses-3.png)")
						h2.page-title.text-center ONSITE COURSES
					.title-st-2.uppercase.mt-20.mb-10(style='color:#444444;') Choose an onsite course if you:
					ul.list-st1.checked.content-p.orange
						li.truncate-on-md can commit to a full time study program
						li.truncate-on-md require a traditional environment to learn
						li.truncate-on-md would like to train overseas
						li.truncate-on-md are seeking a placement in the country of training
						li.truncate-on-md want to study with other students
						li.truncate-on-md don't have stable internet access
					a.button-st1.full-width.uppercase.alt.orange-bg.mt-30(href="#") view onsite courses >
	
